datasets.name: dataset_15
queryLines: SELECT Home_Tile AS Home_Tile, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Tile_Views) AS Total_Unique_Tile_Views, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Tile_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Tile_Clicks, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Views) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Views, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Primary_Button_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Primary_Button_Clicks, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks, MEASURE(Total_Home_Tile_Clicked_vs_Homepage_Displayed) AS Percent_Home_Tile_Clicked_vs_Homepage_Displayed, MEASURE(Total_Primary_Button_Clicked_vs_Tile_Displayed) AS Percent_Primary_Button_Clicked_vs_Tile_Displayed, MEASURE(Total_Secondary_Button_Clicked_vs_Tile_Displayed) AS Percent_Secondary_Button_Clicked_vs_Tile_Displayed, MEASURE(Total_Primary_Button_Clicked_vs_Interstitial_Displayed) AS Percent_Primary_Button_Clicked_vs_Interstitial_Displayed, MEASURE(Total_Secondary_Button_Clicked_vs_Interstitial_Displayed) AS Percent_Secondary_Button_Clicked_vs_Interstitial_Displayed FROM hpx_events_model_homepage_summary GROUP BY Home_Tile ORDER BY Total_Unique_Tile_Views DESC
